Package com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy

Class Pager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ellucian.ethos.integration.client.proxy.Pager
  • public class Pager
extends Object
    Data transfer object (DTO) used primarily within the SDK to easily specify various criteria supporting paging operations. This class follows the builder pattern and contains an inner static Builder class used to build this object with the various attributes/properties.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      static class  Pager.Builder
      An inner static Builder class used for building the Pager object with various criteria.
      static class  Pager.PagingType
      Various paging types to determine what kind of paging to be done.
